    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It honestly breaks my heart a little to post this, but it\u2019s time for my pride and joy to find a new home. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this beauty\u2014it\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single weekend. Seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s an absolute dream to drive, smooth as silk and incredibly responsive. I\u2019ve made sure every inch is pristine because I believe a car like this deserves nothing less. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and cared for by someone who truly knows cars, this is the one. Come on over, let's grab a coffee and I'll show you why this is the cleanest ride in the neighborhood!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional example of the 997.1 Carrera S, finished in Basalt Black Metallic over a flawless Sand Beige interior. This isn't your typical garage queen; it\u2019s a precision-tuned driver\u2019s machine. The M97/01 flat-six has been obsessively maintained with 5k-mile oil analysis cycles, showing zero bore scoring or IMS issues. We\u2019ve optimized the power band with a custom plenum and a high-flow X-pipe exhaust, sharpening throttle response across the rev range. The PASM suspension remains tight with zero bushing deflection, providing telepathic feedback through the corners. Paint depth readings are consistent across all panels, protected by a multi-stage paint correction and ceramic coating. If you demand a chassis that feels factory-fresh with the mechanical soul of a true analog sports car, this is the benchmark.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    }
